{
  "stem": "13623.5",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I don't know who the-- the man was next to me.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "The man died.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "Normally when a-- when-- when somebody died, they used to pick up the bodies or the prisoners that the body died next to, were thrown down to the floor, and they would pick up the bodies.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 62,
      "text": "I didn't throw that body down.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 63,
      "text": "Every time they came for the soup, I would take his arm, and I would sort of fling it.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 64,
      "text": "I flung it-- where the-- where the-- They didn't check because people that were alive looked more like they were dead.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 65,
      "text": "So I would have a little bit of extra soup from this.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 66,
      "text": "Because of this body.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 67,
      "text": "I don't know who he was.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 68,
      "text": "I never-- I don't know his name.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 69,
      "text": "After a while, I couldn't keep him anymore because rigor mortis set in.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 70,
      "text": "I just couldn't keep him there any more.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 71,
      "text": "But it didn't take long with another prisoner.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 72,
      "text": "Same thing happened.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 73,
      "text": "I did this with two prisoners.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 74,
      "text": "I don't know who they were.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 75,
      "text": "I never knew their names.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 76,
      "text": "They-- the ones-- we still had to go out and still stand in that Zahlappell, what they call.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 77,
      "text": "Whether you were weak, no matter what, everybody had to go.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 78,
      "text": "No matter how sick you were, you had to go and stand out on appell.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 79,
      "text": "We started to see the guards, the SS, with white armbands walking around.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 80,
      "text": "Rumor started to say that this meant something that is good in our favor.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 81,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] One day, it's April 15, 1945.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 82,
      "text": "We're standing out on appell.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 83,
      "text": "As we were standing out in appell, a-- two Jeeps of soldiers drive up.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 84,
      "text": "We still look.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 85,
      "text": "We're still stunned.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 86,
      "text": "We're still afraid to move.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
